      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Often made from multihued obsidian, a pyrespike crystal softly thrums like a tiny volcano straining to explode. This weapon crystal functions normally with most solar weapons, but when applied to a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.kCvI3xvm0Q1slajx]{solar flare}<sup>COM</sup>, the crystal grants the solar flare the automatic weapon special property, affecting up to 6 targets. Afterward, the solar flare can’t be used in automatic mode again until you’ve rested for 10 minutes to regain Stamina Points.</p>"
